{"about_the_game":"It\u2019s a new, dark and <strong>machine-filled Edo period</strong>, and the Shogunate rules over Japan with its just, but pitiless hand: <i>you</i>. <br><br>You <strong>follow </strong>orders. You <strong>obey</strong>. You <strong>kill</strong>. <br><br>Until <strong>your sight is taken </strong>from you, and you must learn to \u201c<i>feel</i>\u201d the world anew...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u2014 A world of data and lies</h2>The<strong> Mask of the Oni</strong> creates a simulation of the world around you, but tread carefully: old data will show you only <strong>deceiving echoes of the past</strong>.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294880/extras/Steam_EDA_Cloud-2.gif?t=1728483519\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u2014 Swords sing unseen</h2>Even blind, you are unstoppable. Use different <strong>sensors</strong> to detect your enemies and identify their <strong>weak spots</strong>, then crush them with lightning speed.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294880/extras/Steam_WeakSpot_Cloud-2.gif?t=1728483519\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u2014 Robotic folktales of Japan</h2>Discover the story of dozens of <strong>robotic versions of Japanese folktale creatures</strong>! Find their <strong>weaknesses</strong> and destroy each one with a devastating <strong>finisher</strong>!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294880/extras/Steam_Finisher_Cloud-2.gif?t=1728483519\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u2014 Long-lost mechanical lore</h2>Your <strong>sensors </strong>pierce the curtain of the past. Use <i>sound</i>, <i>smell</i> and <i>heat </i>to explore the world, uncovering centuries of lore and guiding Yami on his vengeful, <strong>story-driven</strong> journey.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294880/extras/Steam_Sensors_Cloud-2.gif?t=1728483519\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Dojo awaits...</h2>Follow the way of the <strong>Cyber-Samurai</strong> and join our Discord community!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ancient Knowledge","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294880/bc5015fc4fa5e29a32e607b15ac5bbbae5e1eb8a.jpg"},{"name":"You are bionic now","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294880/6096aeacaab54a367c0c79a8eaafbc0f90f00d83.jpg"},{"name":"Way of the Samurai","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294880/ce452cf98fddf56845303611440dbb626e72b91c.jpg"},{"name":"True Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294880/67c72c7cebb828b34a6a8196b1f1236d798ed824.jpg"},{"name":"Off the beaten track","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294880/f98590fee6917b3e110766f19a0f82e82d5c7962.jpg"},{"name":"Heavenly King","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294880/3db2314b7eb89652eb325983b4b14df92cbcff6e.jpg"},{"name":"Spirit of the Forest","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294880/93a74eb7f1ed0f0bfb6471bd20114548d13e56a8.jpg"},{"name":"Life of the Dragon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294880/1684abe89bb93243652670cce2d6323d6d519458.jpg"},{"name":"You died","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294880/c320a8107e41776d6b6411d1bc418ac40c6eb20c.jpg"},{"name":"Sword of Justice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294880/fbf67ae26a5769bdde399817829a6371b31a8f1a.jpg"}],"total":27},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294880/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728483519","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asset